{"tid":278401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求肝】母肝衰竭命危未成年兒子欲捐肝無從 求善心人救救母親","createTime":"2017-06-10T11:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T07:24:54.000Z","uid":117054,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d421e2d2fe750ea735e2710f423070fd0b614b70","tid":278401,"uid":117054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497093603_bc1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497093603_bc1c.jpg&h=9e006d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n顏清理現時留醫深切治療部，其大兒子憂心忡忡，在病戶外守候。<br />\n「媽媽好錫好愛我地，我只想她盡快醒返&hellip;我好想送隻戒指畀佢，兌現我對媽媽嘅承諾！」16歲的大哥阿意與弟弟均是中學生，兩人的母親楊太半生為養育兩兄弟勞心勞力，但她近日疑不堪情緒壓力終崩潰，服食過量藥物致肝衰竭昏迷，現於瑪麗醫院深切治療部留醫，急需48小時內換肝續命，否則恐有生命危險。阿意卻因尚未成年致捐肝救母亦無從，加上父親多病，仿如「鄧桂思」事件的翻版，阿意遂透過互聯網及傳媒，只求有好心人捐活肝或屍肝讓媽媽可獲重生！<br />\n<br />\n「媽媽一直用心照顧我們兩兄弟，但我升上中學後卻冇點樣親近佢&hellip;如果媽媽媽今次可跨過難關，我想再一次大大力攬住媽媽，講聲我愛你！」讀中四的阿意雖然正值考試期，但由今日正午至傍晚，他與弟弟及父親一直都守在瑪麗深切治療部之外，憂心忡忡，只因阿意39歲的母親（顏清理）情況危急，急待換肝。<br />\n<br />\n家人稱，楊太（顏清理）本月7日晚因情緒波動曾服食數十粒含「撲熱息痛」成份的止痛藥後嘔吐，肝部因不勝負荷致衰竭，現時她在瑪麗深切治療部留醫，由於解毒藥物無效，急需換肝續命。阿意指，希望有善心人能捐出活肝或屍肝，救救其母親及其他輪候換肝人士。<br />\n<br />\n院方消息則指，楊母現時於O型換肝輪候冊中排第一位，其他在換肝輪候冊中的O型血病人，包括另一名先天性膽管閉塞的5個月大初生男嬰陳俊杰。若有意捐肝救人的市民，可致電瑪麗醫院熱線22553838查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56810995&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56810995%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170610&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTzwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7cfc1bb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56810995%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170610&h=9c79f721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56810995&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170610</a>"},{"pid":"4fa9fc62881d74efd45de2470d637b7e1b59d7cb","tid":278401,"uid":117054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"救人一命 勝七級浮屠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3271f8e2f84684eb6641572db145fc4d043260","tid":278401,"uid":117054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd29c0c3c75c2035f1c79a28310f0340cf881be","tid":278401,"uid":84081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>服食過量藥物致肝衰竭昏迷</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6169718c8ca49eb9de0528aab8242c46bb28d5a6","tid":278401,"uid":117054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"召喚好心嘅連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57acf3ac8b6447b82f16856f671928957c6e612","tid":278401,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>召喚好心嘅連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔捐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2885705ef5006d80d6480f4e2e3f5a22c8197ee","tid":278401,"uid":117054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>服食過量藥物致肝衰竭昏迷</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇得出唔係一般人可以承受嘅壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf929d5954da253dffeefe321f98bfe0fa996af","tid":278401,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply